msgstr "私が死んだ今、全ては失われた..."

#. [message]: speaker=Baran
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:43
msgid "It is over, I am vanquished."
msgstr "終わりだ、私は敗北した。"

#. [message]: speaker=Muff Toras
#: Two_Brothers_With_A_Third_Difficulty/utils/characters.cfg:62
